报错误信息导致的亲属关系或婚姻状况核查不通过等后果，由其自行承担。北京今年首期普通车摇号，超六成指标被“无车家庭”摇中"},"attached_info":"ClUIx8b95ObAwYA0EAMaCDgyMjQzNjU0IJaV35UGMAU4lQFAEXIJNTM5ODI5MDkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d5952653505b4979a3adf9f843bf3749_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1656231213.4944293","card_id":"Q_539810123","target":{"id":539810123,"title":"2 岁女童被保姆遗留电梯后从 8 楼坠亡，该保姆将面临怎样的法律处罚？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/539810123","type":"question","created":1656205262,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":70,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3423,14035,23709,25312,83753],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近期，浙江杭州，一保姆因粗心大意将2岁女童遗留在电梯轿厢内，随后女童独自随电梯升到8楼后，从楼道窗户坠楼身亡。2岁女童被保姆遗留电梯后从8楼坠亡，家长愤而质疑，保姆：接受法律制裁"},"attached_info":"ClQIx8b95ObAwYA0EAMaCDgyMjM5NDc4IM7f3pUGMAQ4RkAScgk1Mzk4MTAxMjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e99bf0e00d91c16520d46bd5aae35e26_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1656231213.4950495","card_id":"Q_426846138","target":{"id":426846138,"title":"沙发怎么选购？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/426846138","type":"question","created":1603353400,"answer_count":70,"follower_count":317,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6854,88734,104305,287411,406695],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"沙发是家居中最重要的物件之一，一定要选择合适的才行，但是选购沙发的坑有很多，到底该如何选购沙发呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ix8b95ObAwYA0EAMaCDU3MTMzOTQyILj2xPwFMAI4vQJAE3IJNDI2ODQ2MTM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail